****Fundraiser 5K Fun Run and 1 mile lil Mustang Run****

Join us at a Fundraiser for Diana Batson and Jesse Horn. This Run is sponsored by Mogollon High School to help raise support for two families that are devoted to our District.

We will start registration at 7:30 am at the Football field. The first 150 runners will receive a t-shirt. The race will be begin at 8 am.
The run will start at the track and run up the canyon, north of the High School.

Cost is $20.00 a runner- proceeds will go to the Batson/Horne Families.

Come out and support these families.
